KLINE, Respondent, v. W. D. WILSON PRINTING INK CO., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 3, 1894.) Action by Arthur' A. Kline against the W. D. Wilson. Printing Irik Company.

Argued before DALY, C. J„ and BISCHOFF and PRYOR, JJ.
